<bibRefCitation author="Kaas" box="[277,548,1058,1082]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" refString="Kaas, P. &amp; Van Belle, R. A. (1985) Monograph of Living Chitons (Mollusca: Polyplacophora), Volume 1. Order Neoloricata, Lepidopleurina. Backhuys, Leiden, 240 pp." type="book" year="1985">
Kaas &amp; Van Belle 
<number box="[488,548,1058,1082]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" value="1985.0">1985</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Two new records reported here are from deeper waters, 
<quantity box="[1201,1329,1058,1082]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.855" metricValueMax="9.89" metricValueMin="9.82" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" unit="m" value="985.5" valueMax="989.0" valueMin="982.0">982–989 m</quantity>
(Panglao 
<number box="[151,207,1094,1118]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" value="2005.0">2005</number>
sta. CP 
<number box="[294,351,1094,1118]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" value="2385.0">2385</number>
) and the deepest record for the species, 
<quantity box="[799,884,1094,1118]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.764" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" unit="m" value="1764.0">1764 m</quantity>
(Panglao 
<number box="[997,1053,1094,1118]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" value="2005.0">2005</number>
